  (12, 'GpnoNw4j1m0', 'Levi Jones Leary shows his preferred berimbolo setup/path, ending in "facebolo" rolling configuration rather than the traditional inversion through.', '2025-12-25T03:29:56.642704', '2025-12-25T03:29:56.642704', 'gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/GpnoNw4j1m0/0.jpg', 'Berimbolo By Levi Jones Leary'),
  (13, 'RscLPT0F-DE', 'Gordon Ryan shows a very technically detailed escape to the body triangle prying the foot after winning a handfighting setup.', '2025-12-25T03:31:53.537042', '2025-12-25T03:31:53.537042', 'no_gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/RscLPT0F-DE/0.jpg', 'Body Triangle Escape By Gordon Ryan'),
  (14, '6Fvs7bH77HY', 'Jozef Chen shows a nearside underhook pass from half guard, explaining his preference in favor of the nearside underhook over the crossface.  In this video, he uses the nearside underhook position to force a half butterfly from a traditional half guard and passes from there.', '2026-01-01T02:18:54.620526', '2026-01-01T02:24:07.111448', 'no_gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/6Fvs7bH77HY/0.jpg', 'Nearside Underhook Pass by Jozef Chen'),
  (15, 'MqVVB3mLCP0', 'Jason Rau shows how how to transition between a "camping" posture and a traditional knee cut to beat the knee shield, finishing with either a knee cut or a forced half guard depending on uke''s reaction.', '2026-01-01T02:27:33.772547', '2026-01-01T02:27:33.772547', 'no_gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/MqVVB3mLCP0/0.jpg', 'Knee Cut Options From Split Squat by Jason Rau'),
  (16, '4WxiXQucLPE', 'Jason Rau explains how to take the back from underhook De La Riva guard by torquing the knee, showing details on how to lock the position into place without needing gi grips.', '2026-01-01T02:31:47.794067', '2026-01-01T02:31:47.794067', 'no_gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/4WxiXQucLPE/0.jpg', 'Back Take From Underhook De La Riva By Jason Rau'),
  (17, 'v83NoavHPyk', 'Jimmy Pedro teaches Yoko Tomoe Nage with a cross step setup, faking a leg attack or forward throw as setup to bend uke forward.  He emphasizes how to throw uke the minimum distance possible to avoid athletic opponents twisting out of the throw.', '2026-01-01T02:39:46.066714', '2026-01-01T02:39:46.066714', 'gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/v83NoavHPyk/0.jpg', 'Yoko Tomoe Nage By Jimmy Pedro'),
  (18, 'mj3z01tAxi8', 'Buchecha quickly shows his preferred torreando variation, knocking the uke back to their back vs their situp and spinning 270 degrees around the guard towards the back.', '2026-01-01T02:48:41.511256', '2026-01-01T02:48:41.511256', 'gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/mj3z01tAxi8/0.jpg', 'Torreando Variation By Buchecha'),
  (19, '7Q23whUc6jc', 'John Thomas shows a number of ways to finish the knee cut and deal with common defenses, including a cross collar cross face with the gi, changing levels to defeat the underhook, and more.', '2026-01-01T02:53:58.613188', '2026-01-01T02:53:58.613188', 'gi', 1, 1, 'https://img.youtube.com/vi/7Q23whUc6jc/0.jpg', 'Finishing The Knee Cut By John Thomas'),
